^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Once again, 4@S over 4@H is "automatic." I would not bid 5@H with jenny's hand. It might be right, but let me explain what criteria to use. Generally, "the 5 level belongs to the opps." What that means is it is rarely right to bid "5 over 5." For example, if I were deciding whether or not to bid 5@S over 5@H, generally I should not bid it. But "5 over 4" is more complicated. |
