NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The most compelling reason to bid 5 over 4 is shortness in the opps suit (e.g. a singleton or void) which Jenny does not have. That is the single most important factor. Not vul against vul, I might do it anyway if I think they are making 4.|
PG| ***** 122 ***** |


NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So based on those 2 factors, Jenny should not bid 5@H. However, she does know they have an 11-card fit and the LOTT is not quite as accurate above the 4-level. But the 11-card fit in and of itself is not a reason to bid 5. On the other hand, at any vul but unfavorable, I would bid 5H with an 11-card fit over 4@S.|
